{"tid":2340184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕節不讓單身狗「受傷」　這間東京餐廳禁情侶消費","createTime":"2020-12-25T08:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T11:34:37.000Z","uid":36494,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e4144503cc0945b6b8fe76f9154f60bb8057274","tid":2340184,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:53:12.000Z","msg":"聖誕節就像另一個情人節，街上總會看見情人一對對，許多餐廳、電影院全被攻陷，但看在無法「放閃」的人眼中各種「羨慕嫉妒恨」，日本一家義大利麵店就為了不讓員工受到「強烈的精神傷害」，近日更有不少餐廳貼出公告表示，「12月24日禁止情侶進入」，引起網友討論。<br />\n<br />\n《日本集合》指出，位於東京都八王子市的義大利麵店「スパゲッティPiaPia」，每年的12月24日都會進行「謝絕情侶光顧」的企劃。這間店的社長以保護員工為由，從4年前開始這個平安夜企劃。雖然有些人投訴店主歧視情侶，又說他的行為很無聊，但社長依然想繼續這個企劃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RX6Xjsh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRX6Xjsh.jpg&h=f5de20d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"311a88f91000a133a2ac660b948a11d205ba20ce","tid":2340184,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:55:26.000Z","msg":"有性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db87361bdc42a77a9cdd888e0fdbb35c409d79ac","tid":2340184,"uid":90499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:58:51.000Z","msg":"社長想保護自己姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a430f29859a554d41e613cc4d3f8e54aabcfbac2","tid":2340184,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aab9abcd801bbf93d25d56458404cf0257f5a84","tid":2340184,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z8tfn07.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz8tfn07.png&h=bc3ba3df&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}